title: Sandra Marton-Not For Sale
description:
Sandra Marton-Not For Sale



USA Today best-selling author Sandra Marton has earned a Romantic Times Career Achievement Award for her catalog of luminous romance tales. Not for Sale stars Caroline Hamilton, a linguist desperate to earn some real money. Enter Brazilian businessman Lucas Vieira, who wants to hire her as a translator and stand-in girlfriend. Considering Lucas' powerful personality, Caroline is more than a little nervous, but she soon finds herself unable to refuse his passionate advances
